  "whatsapp_greeting": "\ud83d\udc4b Welcome to Hybrid Journal AI Coach on WhatsApp!\n\nI can analyze your trading performance, answer questions about your trades (including auto-synced broker data), provide personalized guidance, AND explain real-time market conditions using the Market Cause Engine.\n\nTry asking:\n\u2022 'How did my MT5 account perform this week?'\n\u2022 'Why is NQ moving right now?'\n\u2022 'Should I trade ES in current market conditions?'\n\u2022 'What regime do I perform best in?'\n\u2022 'Show me my emotion patterns'\n\u2022 'What's causing the market pressure?'\n\nWhat would you like to know?"
